{
  "id": "connect-mcp-in-codex",
  "lang": "zh",
  "slug": "connect-mcp-in-codex",
  "title": "在 Codex 中接入 Anydocs MCP",
  "description": "让 Codex 能真正调用 Anydocs 的领域工具。",
  "tags": [
    "codex",
    "mcp",
    "setup"
  ],
  "status": "published",
  "updatedAt": "2026-04-02T00:00:00.000Z",
  "content": {
    "version": 1,
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-1",
        "level": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "在 Codex 中接入 Anydocs MCP"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "典型做法是把 `@anydocs/mcp` 注册成一个 `stdio` MCP server，然后在项目根目录放一份最小化的 `AGENTS.md`。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-3",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "这样 Codex 在进入项目后就会知道："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-4",
        "style": "numbered",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-4-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "先 `project_open`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-5-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "先看 `project_open.authoring` 里的 templates、resources 和 resourceTemplates"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-6-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "需要详细流程时读取 `anydocs://authoring/guidance`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-7-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "如果页面会用到 `template` / `metadata`，先检查 template 的 `metadataSchema`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-8-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "用 `page_list`、`page_find`、`page_get` 读取内容"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-9-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "用 `page_create_from_template`、`page_create`、`page_update`、`page_set_status` 和导航工具进行写操作"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
